;&quot;&gt;Resumen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Permite ver la suma total de un producto en todas las bodegas antes de comprar.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Frecuencia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Media&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Precondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Acceso al inventario general.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:42pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Descripción&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;El sistema solicita ingresar el SKU del material a consultar en la sección productos , El usuario ingresa el SKU del material, el sistema valida que el SKU ingresado exista en el catálogo de materiales, el sistema consulta las existencias del material en todas las bodegas registradas, el sistema recupera las cantidades disponibles asociadas al material en cada bodega. [Excepción 1], el sistema calcula el stock total disponible del material considerando todas las bodegas, el sistema obtiene la información de las bodegas que poseen existencias del material, el sistema organiza la información para su visualización consolidada, el sistema muestra el stock total disponible del material, el sistema permite visualizar el desglose de existencias por bodega, el usuario verifica la disponibilidad global del material y su distribución entre bodegas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:15pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepción 1: El producto no tiene stock en ninguna bodega. El sistema muestra valor cero.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Poscondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Se obtiene la visión global de disponibilidad de materiales.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Dependencias&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-left:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-right:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-bottom:solid #000000 1.125pt;border-top:solid #000000 1.125pt;vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:9pt;font-family: